{"tid":1378691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我好希望香港8月5號會發生《1987:逆權公民》最後個場面","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:01:47.000Z","uid":180201,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"692fc37e2a4a45af971851dcf25d81bc8c5b86d3","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/erqu2OB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ferqu2OB.png&h=ccfafc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到時全港大罷工<br />\n咁次真係全香港遍地開花<br />\n超過200萬零7人（我有可能記錯因爲社會極大無力感而離開咗我地嘅香港人個人數）上街集會（靜坐都得）<br />\n大叫口號：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n撤回逃犯條例<br />\n撤回暴動定義<br />\n撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會徹查警隊濫權<br />\n立即實行雙普選</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yUS0Bj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yUS0Bj.png&h=22ac0ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回看歷史，每個追求民主嘅過程都係會流血，會有死傷。<br />\n就如南韓追求民主嘅運動。<br />\n光州事件嘅逆權司機，到1987年全國上下一心，各有各做，對抗極權。<br />\n黎明前嘅夜晚係最黑暗<br />\n但我地唔驚唔怕 齊上齊落<br />\n好好保護女士、老人家、小朋友<br />\n即使社工、記者都要好好保護<br />\n我地全香港人團結一心<br />\n你班撚樣想分化我地？好難呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，<br />\n加油！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n8月5日 見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23kVYpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23kVYpV.png&h=3708f649&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1dcbca3c4d374547ad01491c7ce35d2f160c416","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"黑警搞完女示威者、婦女、女社工，今次搞小朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abkuovV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abkuovV</a><br />\n#81 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推跌老人家片段</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"552f268168a9050b3b5c1f2020a613981233378f","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0HAYqZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0HAYqZ.png&h=06001efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小朋友中催淚</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4dea3984da3e8834ed7f47c5c52e3305ed6db8cc","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫手推<br />\n多啲提身邊朋友參加8月5社運<br />\n你嘅參加好重要<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地差你咋</span></strong><br />\n[<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWvKRMB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWvKRMB.png&h=41097b3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"528a021110a0b96e044858488106d237477dd60d","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油<br />\n希望大家可以幫推</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67e9143b6df56d203ac8ccc7a9e6c9715350a015","tid":1378691,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd85922f6d6444d2dcf58a8c535f8879f77bb816","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2727dd1b946ac1a33a8948d18fd1a151ef1e8bff","tid":1378691,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e9143b6df56d203ac8ccc7a9e6c9715350a015","tid":1378691,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgm